      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait i'm not pregnant lol i just meant my period is coming up. and a heating pad feels like it might make the throbbing worse though... honestly the pain is pretty intense but i really don't want to go to the ER if i can just sleep through it. is there like a certain dose of the codeine that's safe to take so it just numbs it enough for me to rest? i have some left over from a dentist visit last month",
