      "content": "acetaminophen isn't doing anything for this pain level honestly... it barely touches it. i really need something stronger so i can actually sleep. if i take the codeine with a couple of the ibuprofen tablets together will that make it work faster or something? i just need to get through the night without feeling like my stomach is being stabbed.",
